    my-10 
    py-6 sm:px-8 md:mb-6 md:px-16 md:py-10 
    sm:bg-neutral-weakest  
    border-t-4 border-t-primary 
    sm:rounded-sm
    ">
    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Get the latest Weekly in your Inbox</h3>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base">The <b>15-minutes newsletter</b> on maximizing outcomes for product designers, engineers, and managers. Sent every Sunday morning, just in time for your ☕️</p>
    <form action="https://xyz.us11.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=6dc0c39e37a97ab5a03b51343&amp;id=5c2e4bb0d0" method="post" class="mt-4 max-w-lg flex flex-nowrap justify-center items-center">
